The course introduces informal learning environments and analyses the possibilities for using such environments in contemporary science education. During this course, close cooperation is maintained with the Science Centre, AHHAA, and with other informal learning environments.Objectives/eesmärkid:  1) to introduce informal learning environments and how to use those in contemporary science education;
2) to integrate theoretical considerations about teaching and learning into  teaching and learning in informal learning environments;
3) to acquire experience in working with students in an informal situation.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1) is familiar with informal learning environments and is able to use such environments in contemporary science education;
2) is able to integrate theoretical considerations about teaching and learning into teaching and learning in informal learning environments;
3) has acquired experience in working with students in an informal environment
